ActCanada-Nova Scotia Offshore Petroleum Resources Accord Implementation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment, made by the Canada-Nova Scotia Offshore Petroleum Board, of CHRISTINE BONNELL-EISNOR of Halifax, Nova Scotia, to be the Chief Executive Officer of the Canada-Nova Scotia Offshore Petroleum Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of six years, effective February 21, 2023.
